{"tid":136776,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"羅兵咸永道PwC發聲明道歉攪錯最佳電影","createTime":"2017-02-27T10:21:36.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-28T14:47:57.000Z","uid":41343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"bdfb595458632e92d19bdf4b93d3d7501b5d4693","tid":136776,"uid":41343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-27T10:21:36.000Z","msg":"奧斯卡頒發「最佳電影」擺大烏龍，引起全球熱議為何會頒錯獎？奧斯卡負責計票的羅兵咸永道會計師事務所（PricewaterhouseCoopers）發表聲明，承認最佳影片頒獎人拿到的是錯誤的得獎類別信封，發現時立即更正，並對此錯誤道歉。「我們現正調查為何會發生這樣的事，對發生此事深感遺憾。」<br />\n奧斯卡頒獎晚會在頒獎人華倫比提和費唐娜薇報錯最佳影片名的混亂中結束。本屆奧斯卡最佳影片為《月亮喜歡藍》，但宣佈得獎名單時，竟頒給《星聲夢裡人》，全員上台緊感言時突被叫停，宣布頒錯獎。"},{"pid":"790f6272a23fd71fef290070fd4b704c60675945","tid":136776,"uid":42848,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-27T10:22:45.000Z","msg":"支持下年轉黃龍德 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d063d81703ecdea5e4407064db6e2cd6be1cb50e","tid":136776,"uid":56524,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-28T14:47:57.000Z","msg":"都係叫pwc...pa<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.pwcpa.com.hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.pwcpa.com.hk&d=d2KrXihf468bG0awDawljlKzBYqMCiHg3GgvTcrvEuQ%3D&h=abf29255\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">www.pwcpa.com.hk</a>"}]}